name: Nakoma
description:
A period in my life i was a backpacker . On my trip to  beautiful Vietnam, a cute  little girl from a poor family wore a shiny Mickey Mouse ears hat and her mother was selling flowers, The little girl was drawing  shapes on the floor with her finger, She had no idea about Mickey Mouse and the glamor of the Disney World.


That  paradox led me to draw pictures of girls  in glossy  Mickey Mouse ears hat in my sketchbook,That collection has always inspired me and now I would like to experience that in another way in the digital world.
 I chose the character names from the Walt Disney characters with or without any purpose.
